        <p class="services-p">Prudential resources are another area that regularly causes confusion.</p>
        <p class="services-p">
          The FCA requires certain consumer credit firms to maintain minimum prudential resource levels depending on their permissions and activities.
        </p>
        <p class="services-p">The CCR009 return may include questions relating to:</p>
